An '''Akord Paris''' yw kevambos keswlasek a-dro dhe [[Chanj an hin|janj an hin]] adoptys yn 2015.<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-35084374 COP21 climate change summit reaches deal in Paris], ''[[BBC]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), 13 mis Kevardhu 2015, kyrghys 15 mis Ebrel 2022</ref> An akord a gomprehend sewajyans, aswiwans ha arhas chanj an hin. Bargynnys yw ynter 196 partiow orth an Keskussulyans Chanj an Hin [[Kenedhlow Unys]] 2015 yn [[Paris]], [[Pow Frynk]].<ref name=KU>[https://unfccc.int/process-and-meetings/the-paris-agreement/the-paris-agreement The Paris Agreement], ''[[Kenedhlow Unys]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), kyrghys 15 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

Yn mis Du 2021, 193 eseli a'n Akordyans Framweyth a-dro dhe Janj an Hin Kenedhlow Unys yw partiow a'n Akord. Nyns eus pedwar eseli Akordyans Framweyth y'n Akord Paris: [[Iran]], [[Eritrea]], [[Libi]] ha [[Yemen]]. An [[SUA]] a kwytyas an Akord yn 2020,<ref>Matt McGrath (4 mis Du 2020), [https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-54797743 Climate change: US formally withdraws from Paris agreement], ''[[BBC]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), kyrghys 15 mis Ebrel 2022</ref> mes dasjunyas yn 2021.<ref>Josh Lederman (19 mis Hwevrel 2021), [https://www.nbcnews.com/politics/white-house/u-s-rejoins-paris-climate-agreement-now-comes-daunting-part-n1258304 U.S. rejoins Paris climate agreement. Now comes the daunting part.], ''NBC'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), kyrghys 15 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

An amkan a'n Akord yw finwetha ynkressyansow yn tempredh ollvysel kresek yn-dann dew [[Gradh Celsius|gradhow Celsius]] (mes yn-dann 1.5 gradhow Celsius mars yw possybyl) yn kehevelyans gans nivelyow ragdiwysyansek.<ref name=KU /> An partiow a assentyas ynwedh provia $100bn pub bledhen rag gweres powyow moy boghosek.<ref>Helen Briggs (25 mis Hedra 2021), [https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-35073297 Why is the Paris climate agreement important for COP26?], ''[[BBC]]'' (yn [[Sowsnek]]), kyrghys 15 mis Ebrel 2022</ref>

